snippet.title: Fernbus Simulator | PlayStation 5 & Xbox Series X|S | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
COMING TO CONSOLE SOON | https://fbs.aerosoft.com/

Fernbus Simulator lets you experience the world as a driver of large coaches on European highways and roads in great detail - now on the current console generation as well! Discover many countries and sights from the Eiffel tower in Paris to the Brandenburg Gate in Berlin and even further.

#fernbussimulator #aerosoft #tmlstudios
